%#----------------------------------------------------------------------------
### Setup
%#----------------------------------------------------------------------------

Prerequisites:

  * [Ruby] 1.8.6 or newer.

  * [RubyGems] 1.3.6 or newer.

Installing:

    gem install difects

Upgrading:

    gem update difects

Removing:

    gem uninstall difects
